        <abstract> 
<p>Last letter was written to be passed on for Lushington’s edification. "(Standing on the points of my toes and my tail very stiff)." Is tiring of controversy as a waste of time. Begins to understand CD’s sufferings over <hi rend="italic">Origin</hi>.</p> 
        </abstract>
